                </bibl>
            </div>
            <div uri="http://syriaca.org/spear/837-8" resp="#ngibson">
                <listEvent>
                    <event>
                        <desc> Many of <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/3653">the great and eminent men of <placeName
                                ref="http://syriaca.org/place/10">Antioch</placeName></persName> disguised
                            themselves in poor apparel, carried the chairs of the sick and poor, and
                            provided for them according to their ability. </desc>
                        <ptr target="http://syriaca.org/keyword/dress http://syriaca.org/keyword/disguise http://syriaca.org/keyword/poor http://syriaca.org/keyword/illness http://syriaca.org/keyword/charity http://syriaca.org/keyword/care"/>
                        
                    </event>
                </listEvent>
                <bibl type="primary">
                    <ptr target="http://syriaca.org/work/837"/>
