                    <event>
                        <desc><persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/1977">Paul, patriarch of
                                Antioch</persName> sent money to the cities around <placeName
                                ref="http://syriaca.org/place/2845">Sycae</placeName> to support the
                            ministry to the poor that he had started there. </desc>
                        <ptr target="http://syriaca.org/keyword/money http://syriaca.org/keyword/poor http://syriaca.org/keyword/alms http://syriaca.org/keyword/cities"/>
