                    <event>
                        <desc>Deaconries were established for the men and women who 
                            emulated <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/1977">Paul, patriarch of
                            Antioch</persName>'s zeal and earnestness by serving and giving.</desc>
                        <ptr target="http://syriaca.org/keyword/money http://syriaca.org/keyword/alms http://syriaca.org/keyword/deacons http://syriaca.org/keyword/institutions"/>
                    </event>
